Core Refactoring and Dependency Injection Implementation
The goal is to modernize the core layer of the Waseet project by centralizing dependency management, standardizing error handling, and cleaning up the common tools.

User Review Required
IMPORTANT

The manual dependency injection currently in main.dart will be moved to lib/core/config/di.dart. This will make main.dart much cleaner but changes how Blocs are accessed (via getIt<T>()).

